OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1773342677
OL,3,CResidents take legal action over
OL,4,Cpotential cancer-causing contamination
OL,5,Crisk
OL,7,FITV News' Mel Barham has been speaking
OL,8,Fto locals close to the site of the
OL,9,Fpotential contamination.
OL,11,FResidents living near a former
OL,12,Findustrial site are threatening to
OL,13,Ftake legal action over the presence of
OL,14,Fa cancer-causing chemical at
OL,15,Fproperties in the area.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
