CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1773342677
OL,3,CResidents take legal action over
OL,4,Cpotential cancer-causing contamination
OL,5,Crisk
OL,7,FHowever, land can only be designated
OL,8,Fas contaminated if, under Part 2A of
OL,9,Fthe Environmental Protection Act 1990,
OL,10,Fa local authority determines it poses
OL,11,Fan unacceptable, significant risk to
OL,12,Fhuman health or the environment, based
OL,13,Fon a "source-pathway-receptor" linkage.
OL,15,FAt this stage, no areas of land, in
OL,16,Feither public or private ownership,
OL,17,Fhave been designated as contaminated
OL,18,Funder Part 2A of the Act.
OL,26,@uD@FOUuD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
