OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1773342677
OL,3,CResidents take legal action over
OL,4,Cpotential cancer-causing contamination
OL,5,Crisk
OL,7,FThe presence of PFOA at the
OL,8,Fresidential properties follows further
OL,9,Finvestigations in autumn 2025, when
OL,10,Fspecialists conducted a third phase of
OL,11,Fshallow soil sampling at properties
OL,12,Flocated in proximity to the Hillhouse
OL,13,Fsite.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
