PN,39208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1773342677
OL,3,CResidents take legal action over
OL,4,Cpotential cancer-causing contamination
OL,5,Crisk
OL,7,FThe data is currently subject to
OL,8,Fexpert risk assessment and
OL,9,Finterpretation by the Environment
OL,10,FAgency. This will be shared as soon as
OL,11,Fit is available. Householders whose
OL,12,Fproperties were sampled have been
OL,13,Fcontacted individually and informed of
OL,14,Ftheir results.
OL,16,FIn a statement AGCCE can provide the
OL,17,Ffollowing statement: "AGC Chemicals
OL,18,FEurope, Ltd. has not yet been provided
OL,19,Fwith the details of the Environment
OL,20,FAgency Interpretive report relating to
OL,21,Fthe allotment site.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
