OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1773342677
OL,3,CResidents take legal action over
OL,4,Cpotential cancer-causing contamination
OL,5,Crisk
OL,7,F"However, our highest priority is
OL,8,Fsupporting the community that we live
OL,9,Fand work in, which is why we are
OL,10,Fworking alongside the multi-agency
OL,11,Finvestigation and conducting our own
OL,12,Fvoluntary investigation on the section
OL,13,Fof land at the former ICI site that we
OL,14,Foccupy."
OL,16,FAny residents affected by this are
OL,17,Fencouraged to visit this website:
OL,18,Fhttps://www.wyre.gov.uk/multi- agency
OL,26,@vD@HO]
